{"tid":1800663,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店餐廳想請人","createTime":"2019-12-28T04:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T19:45:41.000Z","uid":6777,"like":26,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"0482eee69994a72b7da2a9e4097750e979ab64a5","tid":1800663,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:47:34.000Z","msg":"幫朋友間黃店餐廳開post請人<br />\n廚房，水吧，管理，幾方面都要人<br />\n<br />\n台式料理，黃大仙區<br />\n<br />\n主要想請：<br />\n全職廚房，有責任心同有經驗的<br />\n$16000-18000,<span style=\"color: red;\"> 好有經驗的可再商議價錢</span><br />\n6天工作，每日9小時，輪班輪休<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地主要想請個reliable 的廚房，兼睇住出品質素，但一直請唔到。好多都放飛機，一係就靠唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想睇下連登既手足會唔會有介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實佢地希望做到個空間比大家聚腳，唔止係食野，而係創作，交流，玩，等等<br />\n<br />\n但就黎唔夠人頂唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n水吧或管理既都請<br />\n兼職水吧，廚房都好需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有提供培訓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣或想了解多d, <br />\n我地tg 再講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc9fd9cd09f1d1a99047d4ea3ca9daadb034aad","tid":1800663,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:49:16.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家問問題，或tg 再講<br />\n解答到既野都盡量答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68bdd8f2ea8046d2d02ae624d7bb79604c5b31b","tid":1800663,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:49:20.000Z","msg":"唔識煮野得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206d06b9ecc1e26f33c3f0f82379d81945cb8aed","tid":1800663,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b68bdd8f2ea8046d2d02ae624d7bb79604c5b31b","tid":1800663,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:49:20.000Z","m